      <title>加拿大债券下跌，因交易员削减降息押注以应对热门 CPI 数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/canada-bonds-fall-as-traders-pare-rate-cut-bets-on-hot-cpi-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于五月份通胀数据好于预期，促使交易员减少对加拿大央行七月份降息的押注，加拿大债券遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/canada-bonds-fall-as-traders-pare-rate-cut-bets-on-hot-cpi-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
